#! /bin/bash
# FS QA Test No. 183
#
# Test to check bulkstat returns unlinked-but-referenced inodes
# (PVs: 972128, 972004)
#
#-----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Copyright (c) 2007 Silicon Graphics, Inc.  All Rights Reserved.
#
# This program is free software; you can redistribute it and/or
